<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Goodbye</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#050816,#111827,#1f2937);
    color:white;
    overflow:hidden;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    height:100vh;
    text-align:center;
}

.stars{
    position:absolute;
    width:100%;
    height:100%;
    background-image:
        radial-gradient(white 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size:40px 40px;
    opacity:.25;
    animation:moveStars 80s linear infinite;
}

.container{
    position:relative;
    z-index:2;
    max-width:850px;
    padding:30px;
    animation:fade 2s ease;
}

h1{
    font-size:70px;
    margin-bottom:20px;
    letter-spacing:4px;
}

#typing{
    color:#00ffd5;
    font-size:28px;
    min-height:40px;
    margin-bottom:40px;
}

p{
    font-size:22px;
    line-height:1.8;
    margin:20px 0;
    opacity:0;
    animation:appear 1s forwards;
}

p:nth-child(3){animation-delay:2s;}
p:nth-child(4){animation-delay:4s;}
p:nth-child(5){animation-delay:6s;}
p:nth-child(6){animation-delay:8s;}
p:nth-child(7){animation-delay:10s;}

.last{
    margin-top:40px;
    font-size:32px;
    color:#7fffd4;
    font-weight:bold;
}

@keyframes fade{
    from{
        opacity:0;
        transform:translateY(40px);
    }
    to{
        opacity:1;
        transform:translateY(0);
    }
}

@keyframes appear{
    to{
        opacity:1;
    }
}

@keyframes moveStars{
    from{
        background-position:0 0;
    }
    to{
        background-position:0 1000px;
    }
}

@media(max-width:768px){

h1{
    font-size:45px;
}

#typing{
    font-size:22px;
}

p{
    font-size:18px;
}

.last{
    font-size:24px;
}

}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="stars"></div>

<div class="container">

<h1>GOODBYE 👋</h1>

<div id="typing"></div>

<p>Every ending is the beginning of a new journey.</p>

<p>Thank you for every smile, every laugh, every conversation, and every unforgettable memory.</p>

<p>Life may take us on different paths, but the memories we've created together will stay forever.</p>

<p>May your future be filled with happiness, success, peace, and endless opportunities.</p>

<p>Distance may separate us, but true memories never fade.</p>

<p class="last">❤️ This is not Goodbye... It's See You Again ❤️</p>

</div>

<script>

const message="Some people become memories... but the best memories last forever.";

let i=0;

function type(){

if(i<message.length){

document.getElementById("typing").innerHTML+=message.charAt(i);

i++;

setTimeout(type,60);

}

}

type();

</script>

</body>
</html>